Plato License
--------------

Plato is a cognitive engine in the form of a class library.

This release of Plato is distributed under the terms of the license, as
specified below. The documentation for Plato, supplied in the "Documentation"
directory, is distributed under the same terms as the software itself.

The basic library functions are written in C++ and are freestanding,
apart from the following library dependencies:

1) PCRE regular expression library.

End of dependencies.

